            </div>
            <h5 class="subheader">
              <a href="http://www.democracynow.org/blog/2015/4/2/economic_disobedience_historic_student_debt_strike" data-clicky-href="#widget/featured/web_exclusive" data-clicky-title="Widget: Featured Web Exclusive Link"><p>Economic Disobedience: Student Debt Strike Expands As 100 Refuse to Pay Back Predatory College Loans</p></a>
            </h5>
            <div class="text">
              More than 100 former students of the for-profit Corinthian Colleges system have joined what they say is the nation’s first student debt strike. The students have refused to pay back loans they took out to attend Corinthian, which has been sued by the federal government for its predatory lending.
            </div>
            <div class="dateLeft">
              Apr 02, 2015
            </div>
